SRC_00670	low	other	src/birth.c	20	1	There are few types of magic more unpredictable and difficult to control than Chaos magic. Chaos is the very element of unmaking, and the Chaos spells are the most terrible weapons of destruction imaginable. The caster can also call on the primal forces of Chaos to induce mutations in his/her opponents and even him/herself.	很少有哪种魔法比混沌魔法更不可预测、更难以控制。混沌是代表毁灭的元素，而混沌法术是你能想象到的最可怕的毁灭武器。施法者还可以召唤混沌的原始力量，诱发对手甚至自身的突变。	"There are few types of magic more unpredictable and difficult to control than Chaos magic. Chaos is the very element of unmaking, and the Chaos spells are the most terrible weapons of destruction imaginable. The caster can also call on the primal forces of Chaos to induce mutations in his/her opponents and even him/herself.",	
SRC_00672	low	other	src/birth.c	22	1	Trump magic has, indeed, an admirable selection of teleportation spells. Since the Trump gateways can also be used to summon other creatures, Trump magic has an equally impressive selection of summoning spells. However, not all monsters appreciate being drawn to another place by Trump user.	王牌魔法确实拥有令人赞叹的各种传送法术。由于王牌传送门也可用于召唤其他生物，王牌魔法同样拥有一系列令人印象深刻的召唤法术。然而，并非所有的怪物都乐意被王牌使用者强行拉到另一个地方。	"Trump magic has, indeed, an admirable selection of teleportation spells. Since the Trump gateways can also be used to summon other creatures, Trump magic has an equally impressive selection of summoning spells. However, not all monsters appreciate being drawn to another place by Trump user.",	
SRC_00674	low	other	src/birth.c	24	1	Craft magic can strengthen the caster or the equipments. These spells can greatly improve the caster's fighting ability. Using them against opponents directly is not possible.	工匠魔法可以强化施法者自身或其装备。这些法术能极大地提升施法者的战斗能力，但无法被直接用来对付敌人。	"Craft magic can strengthen the caster or the equipments. These spells can greatly improve the caster's fighting ability. Using them against opponents directly is not possible.",	
SRC_00676	low	other	src/birth.c	26	1	Crusade is a magic of 'Justice'. It includes damage spells, which are greatly effective against foul and evil monsters, but have poor effects against good monsters.	圣战魔法是“正义”的魔法。它包含许多伤害法术，对肮脏和邪恶的怪物效果极佳，但对善良的怪物则效果甚微。	"Crusade is a magic of 'Justice'. It includes damage spells, which are greatly effective against foul and evil monsters, but have poor effects against good monsters.",	
SRC_00680	low	other	src/birth.c	32	1	Music adepts affect the world around them by singing songs. There are two types of song; some have instant effects, while others have a continuous effect until SP runs out. But the latter type has a limit: only one song can be sung at a time.	音乐学徒通过唱歌来影响他们周围的世界。歌曲有两种类型：有些有瞬间效果，而另一些则具有持续效果，直到施法者的 SP（法力）耗尽。但后者有一个限制：一次只能唱一首歌。	"Music adepts affect the world around them by singing songs. There are two types of song; some have instant effects, while others have a continuous effect until SP runs out. But the latter type has a limit: only one song can be sung at a time.",	
SRC_00681	low	other	src/birth.c	33	1	The books of Kendo describe about various combat techniques. When learning new techniques, you are required to carry the books, but once you memorizes them, you don't have to carry them. When using a technique, wielding a weapon is required.	剑道秘籍上记载了各种战斗技巧。当你学习新的技巧时，必须携带相应的秘籍，但一旦你将它们熟记于心，就不需要再把它们带在身上了。使用这些技巧时，必须装备一把武器。	"The books of Kendo describe about various combat techniques. When learning new techniques, you are required to carry the books, but once you memorizes them, you don't have to carry them. When using a technique, wielding a weapon is required.",	
SRC_00683	low	other	src/birth.c	35	1	The books of Rage describe various techniques. To learn a new technique, you must perform a ritual of rage, destroying the book in the process. Once learned, you may use techniques without requiring the corresponding Rage book, but you will need to find many copies of each book in order to learn all of the techniques.	狂怒之书描述了各种技巧。要学习一项新技巧，你必须执行一场狂怒仪式，并在过程中摧毁这本书。一旦学会，你可以在不携带相应狂怒之书的情况下使用这些技巧，但你将需要找到每本书的多个副本来学会所有的技巧。	"The books of Rage describe various techniques. To learn a new technique, you must perform a ritual of rage, destroying the book in the process."	
