SRC_02775	low	other	src/demigod.c	487	26	Aphrodite is the Greek goddess of love, beauty, pleasure, and procreation. You inherit her sex appeal. As such, your pets are more obedient and shopkeepers fawn over you in their efforts to please you. You may kiss monsters and they might even decide to follow you with slavish devotion, though sometimes this just angers them.	阿佛洛狄忒是希腊神话中代表爱、美、欢愉与繁衍的女神。你继承了她的性感魅力。因此，你的宠物会更加听话，而店主们也会为了讨好你而对你阿谀奉承。你可以亲吻怪物，它们甚至可能决定奴性般地对你死心塌地，尽管有时候这只会激怒它们。	me.subdesc = "Aphrodite is the Greek goddess of love, beauty, pleasure, and procreation. "	半神：阿佛洛狄忒
SRC_02777	low	other	src/demigod.c	502	26	Apollo has been variously recognized as a god of light and the sun, truth and prophecy, medicine, healing, plague, music, poetry, arts, archery, and more. You inherit powers of illumination and are completely immune to light based attacks. You are seldom blinded.	阿波罗被广泛认为是光明与太阳、真理与预言、医药与治愈、瘟疫、音乐、诗歌、艺术、射箭等领域之神。你继承了光照的力量，并完全免疫基于光属性的攻击。你极少会被致盲。	me.subdesc = "Apollo has been variously recognized as a god of light and the sun, "	半神：阿波罗
SRC_02779	low	other	src/demigod.c	514	26	Ares is the bold son of Zeus and Hera, whose very name is feared and respected by warriors and citizens alike. His legendary combat prowess exceeds that of Zeus and Poseidon, but he is less skilled in wiles than the other Olympians. You inherit exceptional bonuses to combat and have a firm grip on your strength. Later in life, you will be able to fly into a berserk rage on command. However, your lust for combat decreases your stealth as you call out challenges to all that you meet. And your resistance to magic is suspect as well.	阿瑞斯是宙斯与赫拉那狂放不羁的儿子，无论战士还是平民，听到他的名字都会感到敬畏。他传说中的战斗力甚至超越了宙斯与波塞冬，但在诡计方面他却不如其他奥林匹斯神灵。你继承了卓越的战斗加成，并牢牢掌控着你的力量。随着你的成长，你将能够随心所欲地进入狂暴状态。然而，由于你会向所有遇到的敌人大声挑战，你对战斗的渴望会降低你的潜行能力。此外，你对魔法的抗性也值得怀疑。	me.subdesc = "Ares is the bold son of Zeus and Hera, whose very name is feared and respected "	半神：阿瑞斯
SRC_02781	low	other	src/demigod.c	533	26	Artemis was often described as the daughter of Zeus and Leto, and the twin sister of Apollo. She was the Hellenic goddess of the hunt, wild animals, wilderness, childbirth, virginity and young girls, bringing and relieving disease in women; she often was depicted as a huntress carrying a bow and arrows. You inherit powers of archery and are very nimble. Your skills with the bow are unmatched and you shoot arrows with increased range and deadliness.	阿尔忒弥斯常被描述为宙斯与勒托的女儿，也是阿波罗的孪生姐姐。她是希腊神话中代表狩猎、野生动物、荒野、分娩、童贞以及年轻女孩的女神，能为女性带来或消除疾病；她常被描绘成一位手持弓箭的女猎手。你继承了箭术的力量，且非常敏捷。你的弓术无人能敌，射出的箭矢具有更远的射程和更强的致命性。	me.subdesc = "Artemis was often described as the daughter of Zeus and Leto, and the "	半神：阿尔忒弥斯
SRC_02783	low	other	src/demigod.c	549	26	Athena is the great goddess of wisdom and the protector of Athens. She was born of Zeus and the Titan Metis, and her cunning far surpasses that of the other deities. You inherit great clarity of thought and magic and will be able to cast spells more reliably than other mortals. And should you fail to cast a spell, you will pay a reduced casting cost rather than the full amount. You also have a firm grip on your mental prowess.	雅典娜是伟大的智慧女神，也是雅典城的守护者。她是宙斯和泰坦神墨提斯所生，她的狡黠远超其他神灵。你继承了清晰的思维和魔法天赋，能比其他凡人更稳定地施放法术。而且，即使你施法失败，你也只需支付较少的法力成本，而不是全部。你同样也能牢牢掌控你的心智力量。	me.subdesc = "Athena is the great goddess of wisdom and the protector of Athens. She was "	半神：雅典娜
SRC_02785	low	other	src/demigod.c	564	26	Demeter is the goddess of the harvest, who presided over grains, the fertility of the earth, and the seasons. You gain powers of regeneration, healing, and temperance. Eventually, you will become resistant to the ravages of time.	得墨忒耳是丰收女神，掌管着谷物、大地的肥沃以及四季。你获得了再生、治愈和节制的力量。最终，你将能抵御时间的摧残。	me.subdesc = "Demeter is the goddess of the harvest, who presided over grains, the "	半神：得墨忒耳
SRC_02787	low	other	src/demigod.c	576	26	Hades is Ruler of the Underworld. You gain resistance to nether forces, increased fortitude and have a firm grasp on your life and health.	哈迪斯是冥界之王。你获得了对地狱力量的抗性、更强的韧性，并牢牢掌控着你的生命与健康。	me.subdesc = "Hades is Ruler of the Underworld. You gain resistance to nether forces, "	半神：哈迪斯
SRC_02789	low	other	src/demigod.c	589	26	Hephaestus was the god of technology, blacksmiths, craftsmen, artisans, sculptors, metals, metallurgy, fire and volcanoes. Like other mythic smiths but unlike most other gods, Hephaestus was lame, which gave him a grotesque appearance in Greek eyes. He served as the blacksmith of the gods. You inherit powers of enchantment and protection. Your equipment will not suffer diminution by corrosion or magical attack.	赫淮斯托斯是代表技术、铁匠、工匠、手艺人、雕塑家、金属、冶金、火焰与火山的神。与其他神话中的铁匠一样，但与大多数其他神灵不同，赫淮斯托斯是个瘸子，这在希腊人眼中给了他一副怪诞的容貌。他是众神的铁匠。你继承了附魔和防护的力量。你的装备不会因腐蚀或魔法攻击而遭受损耗。	me.subdesc = "Hephaestus was the god of technology, blacksmiths, craftsmen, artisans, "	半神：赫淮斯托斯
SRC_02791	low	other	src/demigod.c	603	26	Hera was the wife and one of three sisters of Zeus. Her chief function was as the goddess of women and marriage. You inherit great clarity of mind and capacity for magic. You are very wise and have a firm grasp on your magical energy, which is even augmented.	赫拉是宙斯的妻子，也是他的三个姐妹之一。她的主要职责是作为代表妇女与婚姻的女神。你继承了极其清晰的头脑和魔法才能。你非常睿智，不仅能牢牢掌控你的魔法能量，甚至还使其得到了增强。	me.subdesc = "Hera was the wife and one of three sisters of Zeus. Her chief function "	半神：赫拉
SRC_02793	low	other	src/demigod.c	617	26	Hermes, the Messenger, is the extremely cunning diplomat used by the Olympians to negotiate truces. With his Winged Sandals and his powerful magic, there is no place barred from him, and there is no way to detain him. You inherit great powers of motion and will never become slowed. Your stealth is better than your brethren and your speed will increase with experience.	信使赫耳墨斯是奥林匹斯众神用来谈判停战的极度狡猾的外交官。凭借他的飞翼鞋和强大的魔法，没有任何地方能阻挡他，也没有任何方法能将他扣留。你继承了强大的运动能力，永远不会被减速。你的潜行能力优于你的同侪，且你的速度会随着经验的增长而提升。	me.subdesc = "Hermes, the Messenger, is the extremely cunning diplomat used by the Olympians "	半神：赫耳墨斯
