SRC_02847	low	other	src/devicemaster.c	497	13	Devicemasters are excellent with magical devices, but poor in most other skills. They may shoot or use melee in a pinch, but this will never be their forte; instead, they conquer through their arsenal of magical devices.\n \nEach Devicemaster chooses to specialize in a particular class of devices, and will gain extra bonuses for speciality items. These bonuses include increased damage, increased speed of activation, extra resistance to charge draining, and even the ability to occasionally power these devices without consuming charges; each of these abilities becomes stronger with experience. In addition, speciality devices are easier to use, although all Devicemasters are also good with devices of other types.\n \nDevicemasters have several useful device-related powers; they may detect magical devices from a distance, and gain the powerful talent of Recharging very early on. At higher levels, they gain the ability to move effects from one device to another, or to move magical essences from one item to another if they specialize in Potions or Scrolls. In times of desperate need, the Devicemaster may drain a speciality item of multiple charges at once; this greatly increases the power of the effect, but may destroy the device in the process.	魔导大师（Devicemasters）非常擅长使用魔法装置，但在其他大多数技能上表现糟糕。他们在危急时刻也可能进行射击或近战，但这永远不会是他们的强项；相反，他们通过自己那由魔法装置组成的武器库来征服一切。\n \n每个魔导大师都会选择专精某一种特定类型的装置，并会从这些专精物品中获得额外的加成。这些加成包括：增加伤害、提高激活速度、对装置被吸魔提供额外抗性，甚至偶尔能在不消耗充能的情况下启动这些装置；每一种能力都会随着经验的增长而变得更强。此外，专精的装置更容易被使用，尽管所有的魔导大师同时也精通其他类型的装置。\n \n魔导大师拥有多项与装置相关的实用能力；他们能从远距离探测魔法装置，并在很早的时候就获得了强大的充能才能。在更高等级时，他们能够将一个装置的效果转移到另一个装置上，或者如果他们专精于药水或卷轴，他们也能将魔法精华从一个物品转移到另一个物品上。在极度绝望的时候，魔导大师可以一次性抽干专精物品的多次充能；这会极大地增强该效果的威力，但也可能会在这个过程中摧毁该装置。	"Devicemasters are excellent with magical devices, but poor in most other skills. "	
