SRC_15153	low	other	src/r_vamp.c	6	5	One of the mightier undead creatures, the Vampire is an awe-inspiring sight. Yet this dread creature has a serious weakness: the bright rays of sun are its bane, and it will need to flee the surface to the deep recesses of earth until the sun finally sets. Being undead, Vampires resist nether and have a firm hold on their life force; vampires also resists cold and poison, and darkness only makes them feel at home. Vampires are, however, susceptible to their perpetual hunger for fresh blood, which can only be satiated by sucking blood from a nearby monster.\n \nVampires gain access to various dark powers as they evolve. Of course, they gain a vampiric bite at a very early stage, as they must use this power to feed on the living. Killing humans with this power is also a means of perpetuating the vampire species, and many are the servants of a true prince of darkness! Vampires are rumored to have limited shapeshifting abilities and a powerful, hypnotic gaze.		"One of the mightier undead creatures, the Vampire is an awe-inspiring sight. Yet this "	
